

# ===========================
# Authentication 
# ===========================

### Auth Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":  "admin",
    "password": "admin123"
}

#### Signup
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@hotmail.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}


### Change password
